      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I pop into The Olde Duck for a coffee and carrot cake. I sit outside - much to everyone inside the warm restaurant’s disbelief - to admire the snow covering the Central Drakensberg. I was almost persuaded by another scone, but the carrot cake was definitely the right call. A Dad plays with his two kids, they go inside a small playground and I hear:",
